## WITH CHECK OPTION
* 没有 `WITH CHECK OPTION`

```
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW asia AS
	SELECT name FROM country WHERE continent = 'asia';

INSERT INTO asia(name) VALUES ('korea') # 没有指明continent，可以插入
```

* 有 `WITH CHECK OPTION`
```
CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW asia AS
	SELECT name, continent FROM country WHERE continent = 'asia'
	WITH CHECK OPTION;

INSERT INTO asia(name, continent) VALUES ('korea', 'asi') # CHECK OPTION failed 'test.asia'
```

